NAME
clear_msg - Clears an mgemessage message struct.
SYNOPSIS
#include <mgemessage.h>

void clear_msg(struct mgemessage *msg, const char terminator,
	const char separator);

DESCRIPTION
clear_msg() clears the mgemessage struct. The arguments and message are freed
and the separator and terminator characters reset.

PARAMETERS
msg - a pointer to the mgemessage struct to clear.

terminator - the character to be used as the message delimiter.

separator - the character to be used as the message field separator.

RETURN VALUE
Void.

ERRORS
No errors are generated.

